<br>
There was a knock at her door.  “Lady Minru, a man is here to see you at the front gate,” the servant announced and shuffled off.<br>
<br>
“Oh!! Xoner,” she said to her skeleton, “a man!!  Maybe he has returned from his mission.  Maybe he has come back to see me again!”  Hurriedly checking herself in the mirror, her words came in a rush, “We must make sure that I look stunning for him.  I wonder if he will like my new dress.  Its not black anymore, but I fancy how this dress matches my lipstick perfectly.  Yes, I am ready.  Stay here please.  You know he’s not so fond of you, with your habit of stealing his kills.  I think it is best if I see him alone.”  She ran out of her room, and almost tripped running down the stairs.<br>
<br>
