<br>
He was not himself in this dream. He was not a human who served a god of death and decay but a hero.<br>
 An elf.<br>
 Blurry images of the dark elf woman's beautiful face. Magic and pain. A desperation to survive and save.....someone. The tattered pieces of the dream that was a memory, shatter with the sound of thunder from the sky and rain all around him. The storm makes the raindrops flow around like sheets in the wind.<br>
