<br>
&quot;Comfort is a rare commodity these days, stranger.  But I would be amiss not to invite you in to hear what you find so important to come here to tell me on such a bleak day.  While you go about telling me whatever you have to say, please don't forget to let me know your name, as our servant neglected this bit of information.  Come inside and have a seat.&quot;  <br>
