<br>
&quot; I have an interest in Necromancy.&quot; Morcrin stated. &quot;I also have an interest in lost items of yesterday. I found something. A mask. A mask made from the skull of a large, humanoid. A mask that has a special ability.&quot; The man with half a soul slowly paced back and forth in front of the fireplace, then finally sat down in a comfortable looking chair across from Minru. &quot;Some say the ability is useless. An ability that only works in the right place and only in the right situation. Despite the power of the ability, it's limited use in only the right situations, makes the mask seem....not worth the time to most.&quot; Morcrin looked at the dark elven beauty and smiled. &quot;But not to me.&quot;<br>
