&quot;Since you appear to have little interest in bringing your brother back...or you do not believe I can do so....then you would not mind leaving me a drop of your blood in this vial.....would you?&quot; He could not hide the sarcasm in his level voice, holding up a small, glass vial. &quot;The small portion of your essence may help me.&quot; He did not expect her to comply. He just wanted to see her reaction..or what reaction she would hide. In his mind, he was already planning on what to do. He already had in mind, whom he would contact to assist him.<br>
<br>
